name: AIR ALARM
description:
The air alert means that air defense forces are signaling the movement of enemy aircraft in the direction of the region or there is evidence of the launch of ballistic missiles.

The air alarm will be sounded as many times as the situation requires! It is difficult to determine the exact place where the missile may hit, or which settlement is attacking the plane.

Please move to shelter immediately after such signals! Our armed forces are working on all air strikes to save our lives.
